{
  "stem": "15577.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if they haven't enough, so it didn't interest them to look after this who didn't work, who was-- who was in the region, who they can-- could catch at that very moment, they took them.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the moment the 5,000 were-- were fulfilled, they went away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- and the others were free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it-- it was-- once in a while, we had two or three very, very big so-called akcia, where more-- thousands and thousands were sent away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And most of the Crakow Jews were deported.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At that time, most of the Crakow Jews went to [INAUDIBLE], and they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Nobody survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "From this transport, nobody survives-- survived-- but very, very few who jumped from the trains.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was quite a way from Crakow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So there were very few that jumped and succeeded to-- not to be shot and to come back or to say the story-- to tell the story.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Was anybody from your family part of this akcia?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I should say [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] only my-- my parents and my sister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the family went with-- with one of these akcia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That means sisters-- sisters of my father, their children, parents of my mother, father of my father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the-- all the family were left-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we were left only with three cousins.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When the ghetto was-- was liquidated, and we went to the camp, we were left only my parents, my sister, and me, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my three cousins.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think this is all-- maybe some other-- someone else, but the whole family went with this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I told you, the-- the majority of Crakow Jews went by-- at the end, the ghetto was a very small one.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
